21:40.680 --> 21:41.310
Ponsel.

22:24.000 --> 22:24.590
Ciumlah.

22:25.270 --> 22:26.070
Apakah wangi?

22:27.460 --> 22:28.060
Wangi.

22:28.240 --> 22:28.920
Wangi.

22:29.580 --> 22:30.310
Oleskanlah,

22:36.720 --> 22:38.270
